description: Cases of a mutated strain of Covid-19 have been detected that may undermine future vaccines.
title: Coronavirus: Denmark imposes lockdowns amid mink covid fears
title_page: Coronavirus: Denmark imposes lockdowns amid mink covid fears - BBC News
maintext: But genetic detective work has shown that in a small number of cases, in the Netherlands and now Denmark, the virus seems to have passed the other way, from mink to humans, our correspondent adds.
